column2: Hotel de Suede is a charming hotel in the heart of Paris. It is close to the Rodin Museum, the Musée d'Orsay and Saint-Germain-des-Prés.
Studio design proche Champs-Elysées in Paris features accommodations with free Wifi, 1.2 miles from Gare Saint-Lazare, 1.4 miles from Musée de l'Orangerie, and 1.4 miles from Opéra Garnier.
